{
  "stem": "27507.11",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But for some reason, they came to the conclusion that somebody-- that there was maybe-- that they were stolen goods who somebody just pushed quickly there to hide them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they didn't go into the flat and they didn't search and they didn't find us, which was, you know-- it was all, as I said, a lottery ticket.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was pure luck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And luck and as well the fact that people at Koper's never even dreamt of-- of denouncing us-- on the contrary.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that Marta Koper was an extraordinary person who was looking after us with real devotion and with-- and naturally [INAUDIBLE] as if it was an obvious thing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Never being upset, always being very optimistic, and always getting us food, and always being friendly to us, although her life was as well very difficult.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because it was, after all, this small flat of two rooms and a kitchen, and we had-- on every bed there were two or three people sleeping.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was no place simply to-- I slept with my father and sometimes I slept with my aunt and other people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody had to share a bed almost, and it was altogether crowded out of every recognition.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And during the day, as well, everybody was so crowded together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People were getting on each other's nerves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But somehow we managed to endure all that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in 1944-- in August 1944, on the 1st of August, the Polish uprising started.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Polish uprising started mainly on the other bank of the Vistula, in the main part of Warsaw on the left bank of the Vistula.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then it went on for next two months.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
